dct_title_s: De Wester ende ooster Eemsen met de ander gaten der Zee tusschen Amelandt en Langeroogh
dct_description_sm: North oriented toward bottom left of sheet.
Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margins.
Decorative cartouches, compass roses, rhumb lines.
Shows topography, waterways, shoals, soundings, routes.
Appears in Blaeu's Seespiegel : Insondende Eenkorte Anderwysinghe in de Konst der Zeevaert ..., Amsterdam, 1631.
